short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Real-time monitoring and analysis of AJAX requests in Chrome DevTools

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Moapi Monitor helps frontend developers create and manage API mocks easily and quickly within the browser. With Moapi Monitor, you can create and edit mock responses for any API endpoint, and then use those mocks to test your code without having to make real requests to a backend server.
